      <description>We need only two commands to get a leaflet-map:
 library(leaflet) map &amp;lt;- leaflet() %&amp;gt;% addTiles() %&amp;gt;% To center the map at a certain point:
setView(-58.287691, -33.137864,, zoom=13) %&amp;gt;% To add information at a that point:
addMarkers(-58.287691, -33.137864, popup=&amp;quot;Frigorífico Anglo&amp;quot;) And a picture and more details:
